values:
:3 It's a lucky day for me~ &hearts;&hearts;&hearts; In fact, it was so lucky that I don't even this Friday will get me down. 

What made my day so great, you ask?~

- 'Nee-chan made me the best breakfast without even asking her to~
- I did great in practice. &hearts; Kentarou couldn't find one reason to be grumpy at me.
- The new telephone manga book with LoveCom in it was out a day early.
- My whole family was home for dinner, and both mom and dad cooked~ &hearts;
- I found my other sneaker that has been missing for ages.
- The new Morning Musume PV was on MTV for the first time. &hearts;
- Got a phone call from my grandma - I haven't spoken to her in ages! &hearts;
- It was cooler outside today 'cause of the breeze - thank <i>god</i>. >:3
- Found a clover charm for my cell phone.
- A chance encounter with someone~ &hearts;

He~eh~ And look - this entry was even posted at exactly 7:07. Lucky~ &hearts;
